**Exploring node scripts with React**

I’m thinking we can run a node script alongside React. But for manual tasks, maybe that’s not the right approach. I have to check the file to see how it all connects. It’s interesting to consider the possibilities, but I need clarity on whether this setup really works for what I need. I’ll dig into the file to find out more and confirm my thoughts!
